dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile represents lines of precipitation in Sonoma County, California. These data represent a reprojected version of a precipitation layer developed by the North Coast Regional Water Quality Control Board.This layer can be used for watershed analysis and planning in the Russian River region of California.
